Author: joeigi17
Text: I used to skip eating pretty much all day in highschool till my senior year when I met my bf ... Then he started taking me out to eat all the time now I'm 20 and everyday I feel like I'm just getting fatter and can't stop. I try to go a day or two without food ND just water and it's feels like I'm dying idk how I did it before but I wish I could go back ...
